{"tid":746054,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[真係冇圖]其實香港係多靚女","createTime":"2018-07-17T09:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T21:29:55.000Z","uid":41791,"like":4,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"35770c2f6a42fc5978aae2a0ca7c573180779015","tid":746054,"uid":41791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:19:25.000Z","msg":"呢段野係以華人為主<br />\n唔計白 同 黑人<br />\n其實香港係多靚女<br />\n不論你同唔同意都好<br />\n我係外國生活咗兩年<br />\n外國有靚女比率係比較集中<br />\n其實唔係多<br />\n以香港靚女比率係比較分散<br />\n所以你地覺得唔覺多靚女<br />\n<br />\n行轉旺角 銅鑼灣 觀塘 葵芳<br />\n就會發現 而且每個地方都有唔同氣質<br />\n<br />\nSorry 真係冇圖 我冇可能係街冇啦啦影人"},{"pid":"3ec2af5ff902183f514591c54694fb46a66094ff","tid":746054,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:20:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"d813d006bdaeeb32757909f5e583a13bdbe06f6b","tid":746054,"uid":41791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ec2af5ff902183f514591c54694fb46a66094ff","tid":746054,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:20:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:21:40.000Z","msg":"預咗尖沙咀排到沙頭角"},{"pid":"0cafaf2fcc6ca47742091b390f97e97ed7d84f3c","tid":746054,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:21:45.000Z","msg":"可能因為香港都細呢"},{"pid":"4ea473641de0d53ac40071e632f5275fed5006c6","tid":746054,"uid":188635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:22:32.000Z","msg":"你全家都好靚女"},{"pid":"b6e8d71ae1292cbffe1f84159f725b8232edf1c0","tid":746054,"uid":35621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:23:03.000Z","msg":"多圖=一張圖<br />\n有圖=冇圖<br />\n冇圖=真係冇圖屌你老母"},{"pid":"a7a22e151f5dc261ec08313d3865d1c87ea9ee70","tid":746054,"uid":24203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:23:41.000Z","msg":"無圖你講乜都得啦"},{"pid":"a6369bf330cc1cb42848b118e38dd62499f13219","tid":746054,"uid":126326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"